com.vanillasource.gerec

Interface ResourceReference

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable

    public interface ResourceReference
extends Serializable
    References to resources are the main method by which users of this library should interact with RESTful HTTP resources. All actions to the resources should go through classes from this interface. All implementations should be serializable, without serializing any underlying infrastructure, like caches.
